data.description: This stunning property boasts four spacious bedrooms, each with its own walk in closet.  With 2.5 bathrooms, this home offers both style and convenience.  The open floor plan creates an inviting atmosphere, seamlessly connecting the living spaces, perfect for gatherings and daily living.  You'll enjoy not one, but two living spaces, both offering breathtaking views that enhances the overall ambiance.  The front yard and backyard have been meticulously landscaped, providing a serene outdoor oasis for relaxation and entertainment.  The backyard includes, garden beds, dog run and a shed .  This property combines comfort, functionality, and aesthetic appeal, making it the prefect place to call home
